<section class="system" id="system">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header text-center">
      <h2>The System That Makes Progress Inevitable</h2>
      <p class="section-description">
        This isn't just workouts. It's structure, strategy, and accountability built for your real life.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">✅</div>
        <h3>Custom Training Program</h3>
        <p>Based on your equipment, goals & schedule - designed to fit your life, not the other way around.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">✅</div>
        <h3>Weekly Check-ins + Progress Tracking</h3>
        <p>Regular accountability and adjustments to keep you moving forward, even when life gets busy.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">✅</div>
        <h3>Nutrition Systems</h3>
        <p>Real food, real results - no complicated meal plans, just sustainable approaches that work.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">✅</div>
        <h3>Habits & Routines</h3>
        <p>Build the daily systems that keep you on track, even when motivation isn't there.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">✅</div>
        <h3>24/7 Coach Support</h3>
        <p>Direct access to Jaxon via app for questions, form checks, and guidance whenever you need it.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">✅</div>
        <h3>No Bullsh*t, Just Results</h3>
        <p>Straight-talking approach focused on what works, not what's trendy or complicated.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .system {
    background-color: var(--navy);
  }
  
  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  
  .section-description {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 1.5rem auto 0;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }
  
  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  .feature-card {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }
  
  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--accent-red);
  }
  
  .feature-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .section-header {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
